Create `.tiki/config.json` with the `workflow.tests` configuration section so the markdown commands have a real config to read.

File contents:

```json
{
  "workflow": {
    "tests": {
      "enabled": true,
      "command": null,
      "runOnEachPhase": false,
      "runBeforeShip": true,
      "timeoutSeconds": 300
    }
  }
}
```

Note: PR #101 (auto-healing, sibling branch) creates the same file with a `workflow.autoHeal` section. When both PRs land, a merge conflict on `.tiki/config.json` is expected — resolution combines both sections under the shared `workflow` key.
